      <title>特朗普考虑用德桑蒂斯取代赫格塞斯担任五角大楼人选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-considers-replacing-hegseth-with-desantis-as-pentagon-head</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的团队正在考虑用佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯取代陷入困境的国防部长提名人皮特·赫格塞斯，这一交换将使这位曾经的竞争对手晋升到内阁主要职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/trump-considers-replacing-hegseth-with-desantis-as-pentagon-head</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及将在股票市场上发行最多四家与军事相关的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/egypt-to-offer-up-to-four-military-linked-firms-on-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及总理穆斯塔法·马德布利表示，埃及将在证券交易所推出三到四家军方附属公司，这是广泛出售国有资产举措的下一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/egypt-to-offer-up-to-four-military-linked-firms-on-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:11:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普威胁时，加拿大和墨西哥就走自己的路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/when-trump-threatens-canada-and-mexico-go-their-own-way</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普再次向邻国发出关税威胁前一周，贾斯汀·特鲁多和克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆有机会亲自商讨如何应对这种情况。他们会联手对抗他们的贸易伙伴吗？还是每个人都会为自己着想？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/when-trump-threatens-canada-and-mexico-go-their-own-way</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登宣布为非洲铁路提供 6 亿美元新融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/biden-unveils-600-million-in-new-financing-for-african-railway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在结束对安哥拉的访问时宣布，将为一条多国铁路提供 6 亿美元的新融资，美国希望加大对非洲关键矿产基础设施的投资，并遏制中国的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/biden-unveils-600-million-in-new-financing-for-african-railway</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 13:42:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
