    <item>
      <title>里斯本议会支持就短期租赁举行公投</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/lisbon-assembly-backs-proposed-referendum-on-short-term-rentals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于葡萄牙首都面临经济适用住房短缺的问题，里斯本市议会批准了一项关于终止住宅楼短期租赁的全民公投提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/lisbon-assembly-backs-proposed-referendum-on-short-term-rentals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 12:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党众议院最终计票结果较差，特朗普竞选开局不利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/democrats-flip-key-california-house-seat-as-duarte-defeated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 希望通过 100 天的立法盛会取得成功，但由于最近在竞争激烈的国会选区中失利，以及他自己决定从众议院中挖角自己的支持者担任关键的政府职位，他的这一希望落空了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/democrats-flip-key-california-house-seat-as-duarte-defeated</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 05:56:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
